This center is the one which gives you

00:47:03.020 --> 00:47:04.220
pure knowledge - Shuddha Vidya,

00:47:05.050 --> 00:47:08.230
which works on your central nervous system.

00:47:09.200 --> 00:47:13.030
Then you raise your hand again on top,

