you have to ask for it.

00:53:29.000 --> 00:53:31.170
So now you have to put your right hand

00:53:32.010 --> 00:53:35.090
in the lower portion of your abdomen, press it hard,

00:53:36.240 --> 00:53:38.230
on the left-hand side.

00:53:41.220 --> 00:53:43.150
Now here you have to say,

00:53:44.020 --> 00:53:50.220
"Mother, please give me pure knowledge - Shuddha Vidya."

00:53:52.060 --> 00:53:55.190
"Shri Mataji, give me Shuddha Vidya."

00:53:56.030 --> 00:53:57.110
Please say it six times,

00:53:57.190 --> 00:54:02.170
because this center has got six petals, Swadisthan center.

00:54:03.060 --> 00:54:07.210
"Please give me Shuddha Vidya - pure knowledge."

00:54:17.190 --> 00:54:21.210
As soon as you ask for pure knowledge,

00:54:23.130 --> 00:54:26.100
the Kundalini starts rising.

00:54:28.110 --> 00:54:32.110
