00:54:32.220 --> 00:54:38.120
by opening your higher chakras with your self-confidence.

00:54:39.110 --> 00:54:43.030
So please now raise your right hand

00:54:43.110 --> 00:54:46.120
in the upper portion of your abdomen and press it hard,

00:54:46.180 --> 00:54:48.070
on the left-hand side.

00:54:48.170 --> 00:54:51.020
Keep your feet apart.

00:54:53.200 --> 00:54:55.010
Here,

00:55:00.200 --> 00:55:03.120
you have to say ten times,

00:55:04.060 --> 00:55:06.160
with full confidence in yourself:

00:55:07.020 --> 00:55:12.010
"Mother, I am my own master." Say that, please,

00:55:12.120 --> 00:55:15.190
"Mother, I am my own master."

00:55:16.020 --> 00:55:18.050
"Mother, I am my own guru."

00:55:18.160 --> 00:55:20.070
Because all the great gurus, satgurus,

00:55:20.160 --> 00:55:27.030
have created this center for your ascent.

