And Mother always wants Her children,

00:55:35.180 --> 00:55:39.010
not only what She has,

00:55:39.190 --> 00:55:45.060
but to have much more than Her.

00:55:50.090 --> 00:55:51.190
Now,

00:55:56.120 --> 00:56:00.000
at the very outset I have to tell you

00:56:00.070 --> 00:56:03.120
that you are not this body, not this mind,

00:56:04.010 --> 00:56:06.030
not these emotions,

00:56:06.180 --> 00:56:09.100
nor these conditionings and ego,

00:56:09.200 --> 00:56:13.040
but you are pure spirit.

00:56:16.070 --> 00:56:20.100
So now raise your right hand onto your heart,

00:56:21.040 --> 00:56:24.160
and say with full confidence twelve times,

00:56:25.000 --> 00:56:29.090
"Mother, I am the pure spirit."

00:56:34.030 --> 00:56:39.170
Mother, I am the pure spirit" - twelve times -

00:56:39.230 --> 00:56:46.090
"Shri Mataji, I am the Shuddha Atma."

00:56:47.230 --> 00:56:51.020
With full confidence you have to say.

00:56:58.040 --> 00:57:04.190
I have to tell you that this divine all-pervading Power

00:57:06.030 --> 00:57:09.190
is the ocean of knowledge,

00:57:10.230 --> 00:57:16.010
is the ocean of compassion and bliss.

00:57:17.040 --> 00:57:19.140
You have to say with full confidence,

00:57:19.200 --> 00:57:24.230
"Mother, I am not guilty at all" -

00:57:25.210 --> 00:57:28.210
sixteen times, please say it.

00:57:31.070 --> 00:57:35.150
You have to say, "Shri Mataji, I am Nirdosha,

00:57:35.150 --> 00:57:40.240
I am Nirdosha." Please say it sixteen times.

00:57:44.240 --> 00:57:48.130
Say it for My satisfaction.

00:58:02.070 --> 00:58:11.020
Now raise your right hand on top of your forehead.

00:58:14.010 --> 00:58:17.070
As it is, I have already told you

00:58:17.140 --> 00:58:21.050
whether you forgive or don't forgive,

00:58:21.160 --> 00:58:24.100
you don't do anything.

00:58:25.140 --> 00:58:29.200
So now bend your head as far as possible,

00:58:30.120 --> 00:58:36.040
and here, with all humility, forgive everyone!

00:58:36.140 --> 00:58:38.070
Just forgive!

00:58:38.140 --> 00:58:41.100
Don't think of people who have troubled you

00:58:41.170 --> 00:58:44.200
and tortured you, but just forgive them.

00:58:46.090 --> 00:58:50.080
That's the best way you can get rid of the burden,

00:58:51.160 --> 00:58:53.130
because you are playing into wrong hands

00:58:53.190 --> 00:58:55.080
if you don't forgive.

00:58:55.140 --> 00:58:56.220
Now say it from your heart,

00:58:57.040 --> 00:59:01.030
not how many times but from your heart, please say.

00:59:01.110 --> 00:59:04.050
Many people say that it's very difficult to forgive.

00:59:04.130 --> 00:59:06.050
What is there that's difficult? -

00:59:06.120 --> 00:59:08.140
it's just to say it.

00:59:16.200 --> 00:59:21.090
Now take back your right hand to the back side of your head,

00:59:21.150 --> 00:59:24.230
and push back your head as far as possible,

00:59:25.070 --> 00:59:28.050
push back, as far as possible.

00:59:29.070 --> 00:59:32.100
Here again you have to say from your heart,

00:59:32.160 --> 00:59:37.130
"Oh divine Power, if I have done anything wrong,

00:59:37.210 --> 00:59:39.170
please forgive me.

00:59:40.000 --> 00:59:42.240
If I have done anything wrong unknowingly,

00:59:42.240 --> 00:59:44.190
please forgive me."

00:59:46.050 --> 00:59:49.060
That also say it from your heart.

01:00:01.180 --> 01:00:03.010
Now stretch your hand fully

01:00:08.220 --> 01:00:12.190
and put the center of your palm on top of

01:00:13.020 --> 01:00:16.220
the fontanel bone area which was a soft bone

01:00:17.030 --> 01:00:19.080
in your childhood.

01:00:19.190 --> 01:00:23.160
It is called as taloo, talavyam in Sanskrit.

01:00:24.230 --> 01:00:29.030
Now, put down your head as far as possible,

01:00:29.170 --> 01:00:30.220
put down.

01:00:32.040 --> 01:00:37.230
And now, please try to move your scalp

01:00:39.070 --> 01:00:44.010
with a pressure by pushing your fingers outward.

01:00:44.150 --> 01:00:46.080
Please push your fingers outward,

01:00:46.160 --> 01:00:48.040
put a nice pressure,

01:00:48.100 --> 01:00:53.020
and move it seven times clockwise.

01:00:53.160 --> 01:00:59.000
Here again, I cannot force Self-realization on you,

01:00:59.080 --> 01:01:00.190
you have to ask for it.

01:01:01.020 --> 01:01:02.190
So while moving your hand,

01:01:03.000 --> 01:01:04.030
say it seven times,

01:01:04.090 --> 01:01:08.220
"Mother, please give me my Self-realization.

01:01:09.030 --> 01:01:12.000
Mother, please give me my Self-realization."

01:01:12.060 --> 01:01:14.240
I cannot force it on anyone.

01:02:28.210 --> 01:02:31.040
Please take down your hands.

01:02:31.120 --> 01:02:34.030
Open your eyes very slowly.

01:02:35.060 --> 01:02:36.130
Now,

01:02:40.210 --> 01:02:45.150
put your right hand towards Me like this,

01:02:45.220 --> 01:02:47.080
and bend your head

01:02:47.140 --> 01:02:50.190
and see for yourself if there's a cool breeze

